9-16T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>將咩責任都推哂比人 幾嚴重下</blockquote><br />\n我將自己崩潰既責任推為呢個社會？</blockquote><br />\n你唔想改變=人地係錯<br />\n你崩潰=人地令到你咁<br />\n我唔係話佢地冇錯<br />\n係你完全無視你因為為左所謂既理念唔改變<br />\n又唔接受返你做d個決定既後果</blockquote><br />\n我無錯點解要為左呢個社會多數人係咁而改變</blockquote><br />\n點解你冇錯？點解你係岩</blockquote><br />\n我錯咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b27470c187db611806f898c724a7fbb74fa061","tid":402352,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:54:27.000Z","msg":"先學各方面野令自己成長<br />\n有實力做基礎先有得選擇, 博奕"},{"pid":"e0f7d0942895052991f9299f86b6b7ff44f16442","tid":402352,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先學各方面野令自己成長<br />\n有實力做基礎先有得選擇, 博奕</blockquote><br />\n講到尾都係人脈、關係、社交網絡大於一切"},{"pid":"fdae640bf8354caca480b0536bce01727953cee5","tid":402352,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先學各方面野令自己成長<br />\n有實力做基礎先有得選擇, 博奕</blockquote><br />\n講到尾都係人脈、關係、社交網絡大於一切</blockquote><br />\nYes, 但要有實力既人做你朋友<br />\n先要自己有實力<br />\n有利用價值人地先睇得起你"},{"pid":"f67e93a31368e2b5fa3c05db59c57c5f6b0549ec","tid":402352,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:28:04.000Z","msg":"每一日都唔好做會令自己後悔嘅事"},{"pid":"ec2451a7f15a936d48b1961d2716c84ab73b5ac9","tid":402352,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T02:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3220b4bec0bc98c50e172fe2f7640ce87225b13e","tid":402352,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔講無謂嘅大話<br />\n但係必要時會講</blockquote><br />\nExactly same<br />\n平時唔講大話，到真係需要講嗰時先會有人信你嘅大話</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我成日都咁樣同人